ZH: 我花了很长时间撰写这篇文章。
EN: I spent a long time on writing this article.

ZH: 他花费了整个下午撰写他的新小说。
EN: He spent the whole afternoon writing his new novel.

ZH: 这个作家很有天赋，可以迅速撰写出杰出的作品。
EN: This writer is very talented, able to quickly write outstanding works.

ZH: 我们需要准备撰文关于环保的议题。
EN: We need to prepare an article on environmental protection.

ZH: 他的撰文风格独特而生动。
EN: His writing style is unique and vivid.

ZH: 这篇撰文引起了广泛的关注。
EN: This article has attracted widespread attention.

ZH: 她是杂志社的主编，经常在杂志上撰写专栏。
EN: She is the editor-in-chief of a magazine, often writing columns in the magazine.

ZH: 这本书主要撰写关于历史事件的分析。
EN: This book mainly writes about the analysis of historical events.

ZH: 我们需要一支擅长撰写商业报道的团队。
EN: We need a team that is good at writing business reports.

ZH: 他撰写的这篇评论引发了热烈的讨论。
EN: The commentary he wrote sparked heated debates.

ZH: 这个学生很擅长撰写诗歌。
EN: This student is very good at writing poetry.

ZH: 教授花了几周的时间撰写他的学术论文。
EN: The professor spent several weeks writing his academic paper.

ZH: 她被邀请撰写一篇关于青少年心理健康的文章。
EN: She was invited to write an article on the mental health of teenagers.

ZH: 这个项目需要一个团队来撰写详细的报告。
EN: This project requires a team to write detailed reports.

ZH: 在写作之前，作者经常先撰写大纲和提纲。
EN: Before writing, authors often write outlines and summaries.

ZH: 这篇深度撰文对这一问题进行了深入分析。
EN: This in-depth article provides a thorough analysis of the issue.

ZH: 这家报社需要撰写有关政治和经济问题的文章。
EN: This newspaper needs to write articles on political and economic issues.

ZH: 她的撰文技巧使她成为了一名出色的记者。
EN: Her writing skills have made her an outstanding journalist.

ZH: 这个项目需要一篇有关市场趋势的高质量撰文。
EN: This project requires a high-quality article on market trends.

ZH: 作家花费了数月撰写他的长篇小说。
EN: The writer spent several months writing his novel.
